OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784663291
OL,3,CSir Alex Ferguson pays tribute to
OL,4,Cgreat rival Kevin Keegan
OL,6,FSir Alex Ferguson has paid tribute to
OL,7,Fhis fierce managerial rival who built
OL,8,FNewcastle's "best ever team" amid an
OL,9,Fongoing outpouring of affection for
OL,10,FKevin Keegan.
OL,12,FThe former Manchester United boss, who
OL,13,Fwas famously on the other end of
OL,14,FKeegan's "I'd love it, absolutely love
OL,15,Fit, if we beat them" rant revealed his
OL,16,Fhuge respect for the former Magpies
OL,17,Fmanager following his death.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
