CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784663291
OL,3,CSir Alex Ferguson pays tribute to
OL,4,Cgreat rival Kevin Keegan
OL,6,FKeegan died aged 75 after a battle
OL,7,Fwith cancer, prompting tributes to the
OL,8,Fformer Scunthorpe, Liverpool, Hamburg,
OL,9,FSouthampton and Newcastle frontman
OL,10,Ffrom across the football community.
OL,12,FSpeaking to Track Radio, Ferguson
OL,13,Fsaid: "I had the utmost respect for
OL,14,Fhim. We had many duels when he was
OL,15,Fmanager of Newcastle, but I have to
OL,16,Fsay the job he did at Newcastle was
OL,17,Ffantastic.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784663291
OL,3,CSir Alex Ferguson pays tribute to
OL,4,Cgreat rival Kevin Keegan
OL,6,F"He re-energised that club and he
OL,7,Fbrought that enthusiasm and fanaticism
OL,8,Fthat great supporters can give. That's
OL,9,Fthe job he did.
OL,11,F"And he also brought three great
OL,12,Fplayers to the club ` (David) Ginola,
OL,13,F(Faustino) Asprilla, Philippe Albert `
OL,14,Fand added a bit of class to the team,
OL,15,Fand I must say the challenges we had
OL,16,Fwith Newcastle at that time at United
OL,17,Fwere huge.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784663291
OL,3,CSir Alex Ferguson pays tribute to
OL,4,Cgreat rival Kevin Keegan
OL,6,F"Kevin carried the love of the game on
OL,7,Fhis sleeve, there's no question about
OL,8,Fthat, and that carried right on to the
OL,9,Ffans, to the players.
OL,11,F"That period at Newcastle was of
OL,12,Femotion, it was excitement. They
OL,13,Fbrought these great players to the
OL,14,Fclub too and they added to it, and it
OL,15,Fgave Newcastle ` I think ` their best
OL,16,Fever team."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784663291
OL,3,CSir Alex Ferguson pays tribute to
OL,4,Cgreat rival Kevin Keegan
OL,6,FFerguson's Manchester United
OL,7,Fultimately snatched the Premier League
OL,8,Ftitle from Keegan's Newcastle in April
OL,9,F1996, which lead to an emotional post-
OL,10,Fmatch interview.
OL,12,FHowever Ferguson revealed they later
OL,13,Fbumped into each other in a pub in
OL,14,FSurrey after the season had ended and
OL,15,Fspent the night around a piano - with
OL,16,Fthoughts of football rivalry shelved.
OL,18,FFerguson said: "The great thing about
OL,19,Fhim, he held no grudges. That was a
OL,20,Ffantastic quality he had and we had a
OL,21,Fgreat night.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784663291
OL,3,CSir Alex Ferguson pays tribute to
OL,4,Cgreat rival Kevin Keegan
OL,6,F"All aside whatever happened in
OL,7,Fprevious weeks, that was soon
OL,8,Fforgotten. I really respected him for
OL,9,Fthat."
OL,11,FAn outpouring of love followed the
OL,12,Fannouncement of Keegan's death on 20
OL,13,FJuly, including from his former club
OL,14,FNewcastle United, who called him "the
OL,15,Fbeating heart of the club for
OL,16,Fgenerations of supporters".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784663291
OL,3,CSir Alex Ferguson pays tribute to
OL,4,Cgreat rival Kevin Keegan
OL,6,FThe England National team also paid
OL,7,Ftribute to the former forward,
OL,8,Fannouncing his life will be celebrated
OL,9,Fwhen the Three Lions take on Spain in
OL,10,Ftheir first Nations League match in
OL,11,FSeptember.
OL,13,FSir Trevor Brooking, who played
OL,14,Falongside him for England, said in a
OL,15,Fstatement: "I am so very sad to hear
OL,16,Fthe devastating news about my friend
OL,17,Fand former team-mate Kevin Keegan.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784663291
OL,3,CSir Alex Ferguson pays tribute to
OL,4,Cgreat rival Kevin Keegan
OL,6,F"My friendship with Kevin goes back
OL,7,Fmany decades, to our playing days for
OL,8,FEngland. We were lucky enough to
OL,9,Fdevelop a real understanding on the
OL,10,Ffield of play and know what each other
OL,11,Fwas thinking.
OL,13,F"Kevin liked to run and find space on
OL,14,Fthe pitch and I'd try to time my
OL,15,Fpasses to give him the best chance to
OL,16,Fuse his world-class skills to score.
OL,18,F"We roomed together on England duty
OL,19,Fand Kevin, with his bubbly character,
OL,20,Fwas never shy of making jokes, often
OL,21,Fat my expense!
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784663291
OL,3,CSir Alex Ferguson pays tribute to
OL,4,Cgreat rival Kevin Keegan
OL,6,F"I recently met up for lunch with
OL,7,FKevin and Jean when they were visiting
OL,8,FLondon. Although it had been a while
OL,9,Fsince we'd last seen each other, we
OL,10,Fpicked up our conversation as if it
OL,11,Fhad been yesterday.
OL,13,F"That afternoon, reminiscing about our
OL,14,Ffootballing days, is one I will always
OL,15,Ftreasure.
OL,17,F"Our thoughts and love are with Jean,
OL,18,FLaura, Sarah and all of Kevin's family
OL,19,Fat this sad time."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
